<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.10">
<l>maṇṇu ḷārpukaḻ vētiyar nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamattuḷ</l>
<l>aṇṇal cēvaṭik kīḻaṭain tuyntava ṉālima ṉaruḷmāri</l>
<l>paṇṇu ḷārtarap pāṭiya pāṭalip pattumval lārulakil</l>
<l>eṇṇi lātapē riṉpamuṟ ṟimaiya varōṭuñ kūṭuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten songs which Āli’s king, a beneficent cloud,</l>
<l rend="indent">sang so [they] naturally abounded in music,</l>
<l>The one who obtained bliss reaching low at the rosy feet</l>
<l rend="indent">of the great lord in Vaṉpuruṭōttamam</l>
<l>In Nānkūr with Vedic experts whom those of the earth praise,</l>
<l>Having experienced innumerable great delight in the world,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will join with the unblinking [celestials].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
